,"2026-07-08T09:00:00.000Z"],[18,19,20],"running","fitness","beginner",false,"/images/miles-1.png","The Couch to 5K program is scientifically designed to take beginners from sedentary to running 5K in just 9 weeks.\n\n![Her Miles](/images/miles-1.png)\n\n## Understanding the Program\nAlternate running and walking for gradually increasing intervals.\n\n## Weekly Breakdown\nWeeks 1-3: Heavy walking, light running\nWeeks 4-6: Balanced intervals\nWeeks 7-9: Predominantly running\n\n## Getting Started\nInvest in proper running shoes and find a safe route.\n\nYou've got this—every runner started as a beginner!\n\n![Her Miles](/images/miles-2.png)","src/content/blog/couch-to-5k-guide.md","57d4d8840e745a39",{"html":27,"metadata":28},"\u003Cp>The Couch to 5K program is scientifically designed to take beginners from sedentary to running 5K in just 9 weeks.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/miles-1.png\" alt=\"Her Miles\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"understanding-the-program\">Understanding the Program\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Alternate running and walking for gradually increasing intervals.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"weekly-breakdown\">Weekly Breakdown\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Weeks 1-3: Heavy walking, light running\nWeeks 4-6: Balanced intervals\nWeeks 7-9: Predominantly running\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"getting-started\">Getting Started\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Invest in proper running shoes and find a safe route.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You’ve got this—every runner started as a beginner!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/miles-2.png\" alt=\"Her Miles\">\u003C/p>",{"headings":29,"localImagePaths":40,"remoteImagePaths":41,"frontmatter":42,"imagePaths":45},[30,34,37],{"depth":31,"slug":32,"text":33},2,"understanding-the-program","Understanding the Program",{"depth":31,"slug":35,"text":36},"weekly-breakdown","Weekly Breakdown",{"depth":31,"slug":38,"text":39},"getting-started","Getting Started",[],[],{"title":14,"description":15,"pubDate":43,"tags":44,"draft":21,"image":22},["Date","2026-07-0